<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="once-conj">once <strong><em>conj</em></strong> ★</h1>
<p>英 /wʌns/    美 /wʌns/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>一旦… (就…)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Once you form a bad habit, it’s very difficult to get rid of it.
一旦养成了坏习惯，你就很难改掉它。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li><strong><em>_</em></strong>_ (一旦) the damage is done, it will take many years for the farmland to recover.  （2015 北京改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. Once  </p></div>